gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Great sages are blessed by God, their wish fulfilled in a hundred years; 
Similarly, we have been forsaken by God, our understanding revealed to us within.

Its end is fixed, it will not become abundant or infinite; 
The difference is in the left arm and right arm is like a nest; 
One gets bitter dreams of a donkey, grief follows.

Here is the translation:

The reward of the mantra's worship has been given, virtues have been obtained through it;  
Ati Kaliyo's hair gets separated, Sindur's thread is taken as punishment.

Here is the translation:

He came with Lord's grace around him, who is with children and has a fight; 
Lord was angry with His mother, took her by the hand to destroy.

Here is the translation:

My own eat, eat, and again my own forget the lawsuit; 
Famished faces bloomed with arms, Hari Upper one did many wrath.

Here is the translation:

We went to Ekadashi's vigil, and from there we came to our homes; 
It was seen that no child was born there, the religion got decayed at that time.

Here is the translation:

Worshiped devotion is lamenting the Lord's name there, comes to that place and says; 
Who has ruined you, O couple, asks, tell of your calamity there.

Today I won't let it go by its name, will come back to this place; 
Today my path is blocked, seems right in front of me, 
I'll go far away with a glance, out of sight.

Here is the translation:

This said, virtues are not done, know the misery of a demon's state; 
It was said to Kalidatt's place, and that child will not be destroyed.

Here is the translation:

In my hands is a child of devotion, that's what time says; it has passed away, the couple happy together, that's what time says;
Devotion says listen to Hanuman, there is no other hope than this, destruction awaits.
